<span class="hl_good"><span class="hl_keyword">lemma</span> Strong_Forward_Secrecy_key [use_induction]:<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;all-traces<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;<span class="hl_operator">∀ </span>A B X Y key #i<span class="hl_operator">.</span><br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="hl_operator">(</span>Commit( A, B, &lt;X, Y, key&gt; ) <span class="hl_operator">@</span> #i<span class="hl_operator">)</span> <span class="hl_operator">⇒</span><br/>
